resources.description: The file contains a matching of municipalities of the country program "Kapodistrias", with new municipalities, as defined in the "Kallikrates." The version of the data is 1.1 (ver. 1.1). The Data are based on the prior version (ver. 1.0) to which were added: 1)The YPES codes for Kapodistrian Municipalities OTA, 2)The YPESAHD codes for Municipalities of Kallikrates, 3)The ESYE/ELSTAT codes for Kapodistrian OTA, 4)The ELSTAT codes for Municipalities of Kallikrates in XLS.
resources.name: Municipalities Catalogue (List of municipalities) in XLS.
